title: I Know I'm 1 Year Late But...
body:
This is what happens when you've been inactive on LoL and play on a new summoner's rift.
http://31.media.tumblr.com/62c74ac3bfc07f8ae89739199e0263b7/tumblr_inline_nw4d6fvxoE1sf7uwi_500.gif

replies.body: This is also junglers every time the jungle is updated. It can be rough.

God damn it, every god damn year I have to relearn the jungle, is so annoying, now that we have Baron JR, it's been rough to remember him, I always end up killing him at the 17/18 min mark, when I finally think "Wait why has baron spawned? ohhhh Right, lets get him!"

i always remember him...but no one will help me, and hes too tough to solo early...doesnt matter how many are dead, they just dont care hes there...probably because they havent seen him prioritized in lcs matches yet..im sure by the end of the spring split, rift herald will be the early objective and everyone will die around it instead of baron, lol

this place is cursed!
Don't worry its still the rift.. Just shinier.
Plus Herald,Dragon buffs,Scuttler,Laser turrets,and Jesus minions on baron buff
Yep. that's how i feel too. Though i still mostly play ARAM.
